# Walkthrough — GoLive Phase 9: UI & Discovery Polish

## Summary
Major UI overhaul across four key pages plus supporting infrastructure.

---

## Changes Made

### 1. Home Page ([page.tsx](file:///C:/GoLive/app/page.tsx))
- **Hero Banner**: Top-viewed video displayed as a cinematic banner with gradient overlay
- **Skeleton Loaders**: 8 shimmer placeholders while data loads
- **Category Chips**: Icons, blur backdrop, and shadow on active state
- **Section Headers**: "Recommended" / category name with trending link
- **Empty State**: Illustrated CTA with Upload button

### 2. VideoCard ([VideoCard.tsx](file:///C:/GoLive/components/VideoCard.tsx))
- **Animated Entrance**: `fade-in` + `slide-in-from-bottom` on mount
- **Gradient Hover**: Bottom-to-top dark overlay on thumbnail hover
- **Progress Bar Shimmer**: Purple bar expands on hover
- **Avatar Ring**: Glows primary on hover
- **Formatted Stats**: "1.2K views · 2h ago" via [formatViews](file:///C:/GoLive/lib/utils.ts#5-16) + [timeAgo](file:///C:/GoLive/lib/utils.ts#17-40)

### 3. Trending Page ([page.tsx](file:///C:/GoLive/app/trending/page.tsx))
- **Real Data**: Fetches from Supabase `videos` table, sorted by `view_count` descending
- **Time-Range Tabs**: Today / This Week / This Month with active pill styling
- **Rank System**: Gold/Silver/Bronze trophies for top 3, gradient row backgrounds
- **Loading/Empty States**: Spinner and illustrated empty state

### 4. Upload Page ([page.tsx](file:///C:/GoLive/app/upload/page.tsx))
- **Native File Inputs**: Removed `react-dropzone` dependency for reliability
- **Thumbnail Preview**: Live image preview when a thumbnail is selected
- **Progress Bar**: Animated gradient bar with step labels ("Uploading video...", "Publishing...")
- **Success State**: Animated confirmation with "Go Home" / "Upload Another" actions
- **Character Counters**: Title (100) and Description (5000) limits

### 5. Utilities ([utils.ts](file:///C:/GoLive/lib/utils.ts))
- [formatViews(count)](file:///C:/GoLive/lib/utils.ts#5-16) → "1.2K", "3.4M"
- [timeAgo(dateString)](file:///C:/GoLive/lib/utils.ts#17-40) → "2h ago", "3d ago"

### 6. Skeleton Component ([VideoCardSkeleton.tsx](file:///C:/GoLive/components/VideoCardSkeleton.tsx))
- Pulsing placeholder matching VideoCard layout
